I want you to know that it's okay to feel bad, tired or nothing at all, to lose hope, to give up, to want to end it all. Nobody can make what you feel invalid or false. It's you, it's the way you deal with all the good and bad stuff life has brought in your way. It's your choices, it's your life. Of course, there will always be moments that you feel like nothing matters anymore and it will be true. Maybe it's all pointless. But what if it isn't? What if we can create the point in our lives? I don't know if it matters, if it will lead to anything, but I've seen you getting through hard times and I believe in you, I believe that you can make it out of the dark again. Only if you want to. The fact that I believe in you doesn't mean you are obliged to keep trying. I know you probably don't care, it's often hard to see anything good in some situations and being negative is normal. But you could stay in this struggle for a while or for longer and understand that in the end, it all happens to teach you a lot and make you stronger. You don't know what can suddenly change. Take your time, make your decisions. I'm here for you! ❤
@emmawatson #emmawatson

